{"tid":1550882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[置頂]20190908邊個衝美領就係鬼","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:42:26.000Z","uid":40663,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"48a501e9f37301912429999d378119fff3614bd6","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:21:33.000Z","msg":"聽日就係集會同遊行<br />\n想再提醒下各位手足<br />\n我地去美領<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係抗議</span></span><br />\n我地係表達我地嘅請求，係「求」<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以衝</span></strong></span><br />\n亦都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇需要衝</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我本人極度唔同意主動捉鬼<br />\n但聽日，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個衝邊個就係鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個衝邊個就係鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個衝邊個就係鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我地聽日見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8hCKO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8hCKO6.jpg&h=d89285cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGUhKO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGUhKO6.jpg&h=bb655f34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9upBfVN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9upBfVN.jpg&h=bc2d7d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec784278cf01d0dd5d6996a184c02fb47f672403","tid":1550882,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92cda9aacf6bc752aba3bff9669d75e3eb71dfac","tid":1550882,"uid":160247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:22:07.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"675e18d176cb1d3d50be990bbb229373b4806adb","tid":1550882,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ae7d6518\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"a2addd83087f486f08572572bfee85e18ae90806","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"648046ba575065e5f73a3494789ccd35997cc848","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b49951148af6ba18191ac3de215e57d731722c02","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea2ba36bd915ba9ba0a4790a2004371eab2ca3f4","tid":1550882,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:45.000Z","msg":"【更新/置頂】9月8日集會遊行有不反對通知書！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549876</a><br />\n<br />\n熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟推兩野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agKgKyV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agKgKyV</a><br />\n<br />\n[頂置]908必須過百萬，請大家優先開/推908post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549103</a><br />\n<br />\n請分享出去俾外國既文宣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agKifoV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agKifoV</a>"},{"pid":"879c915c70552ebbfc42beee8e6a3476e22a39f0","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9af6ad98f147434d42c2a1421853131cca8788d9","tid":1550882,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟推兩野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3262c0034912ccd2695822d48a1c61bb56cec968","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep