題用捉鬼呢個concept<br />\n好多連登仔唔睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個唔覺意又屈你捉鬼 <br />\n同埋成日提住唔係咁好<br />\n建議下次唔衝ge活動標題可以試下溫和d<br />\neg 20190908遊行去美領 唔做其他野<br />\n(sorry for唔識改標題<br />\n內文先打番唔好衝 邊個衝邊個係鬼<br />\n咁樣應該會好睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeab0753568dbff741ada714cb9fe02103ae149a","tid":1550882,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！<br />\n連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n今日 下午 美國領事館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=a431f684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"d54f69de07f6e8d58f3aabcb24f4339f42ab81c6","tid":1550882,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"終極和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7364c984001ae2eb5815f7e7fa8396601ba07a3","tid":1550882,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"898e34ca4a6e145f81903ab401aef54ee2540c3c","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04930ba6694ab3ae26e3c51ff12f5e61dbc8a288","tid":1550882,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"addf588f075891985e47bdb2bbef25f1cfe71f0b","tid":1550882,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58c7054f9981c470c9fa432af57bfe34913bf53d","tid":1550882,"uid":7524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:12:57.000Z","msg":"推, 邊個搞美領一定要捉住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:54:22.000Z","msg":"唔係順手推d鬼入美領仲好咩？<br />\n<br />\n美國領土內等美帝慢慢招呼佢哋。"},{"pid":"6bb2ac6130d3a1c7a8636e41b58d267f9a74cdc3","tid":1550882,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識唱嘅大家一齊唱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=be40449e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《願榮光歸香港》  </strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">As we yearn, our freedom nighs</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With eyes blinded, long it comes the night</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight</span><br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!</span><br />\n捍自由   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We shall strike</span><br />\n來齊集這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">This perilous night</span><br />\n來全力抗對  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With hope, with song, with dignity!</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4kAzyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4kAzyW.jpg&h=84f48da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英文譯版原post<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》英文歌詞 &quot;Glory be to Thee, Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547782\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547782</a></span>"},{"pid":"e9c2ec620923da986cc41401b617c70b86caf08b","tid":1550882,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f5f7c3f97c314eccc0715f293d097d424c71a9","tid":1550882,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets